These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different games are played: go, scrabble, whist, poker
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person playing go is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person playing scrabble##2
4. the person playing poker is on the far left##1
5. the person playing whist is between the person playing scrabble and the person playing go##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Game   | poker         | scrabble   | whist | go       |
| Sport      | weightlifting | cycling | soccer   | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, poppy, daffodil, bellflower
1. the person who growsbellflower is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who growspoppy##2
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | gardening | reading | video-games |
| Flower   | poppy    | bellflower   | balloon-flower | daffodil       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, corn, cranberry, kale
House: cottage, tower, palace, victorian
1. the palace house is on the right of the person eating kale##1
2. the palace house is between the tower house and the person eating corn##2
3. the tower house is on the far left##1
4. the victorian house is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
5. the person eating corn is the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | kale    | cauliflower | corn   | cranberry  |
| House   | tower | palace   | victorian | cottage |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, november, march, january
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, biathlon, rugby, tennis
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person who's birthday is in january##2
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Birthday     | january   | july    | march       | november   |
| Sport   | rugby | tennis | basketball | biathlon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, blues, dubstep, indie
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the fan of dubstep is on the far left##1
3. the fan of techno is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is between the fan of techno and the fan of blues##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Beverage   | fanta        | iced-tea | soy-milk  | hot-chocolate |
| Music-Genre      | dubstep | blues  | indie | techno    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, d&b, pop, salsa
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, dutch, colombian, brazilian
1. the colombian is on the right of the dutch##1
2. the fan of salsa is the colombian##1
3. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
4. the fan of d&b is the mexican##1
5. the fan of pop is between the fan of classical and the fan of d&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | pop           | classical | salsa  |
| Nationality         | mexican | brazilian | dutch   | colombian |

