.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, gospel, house, punk
4 different pets are kept: ferret, goat, bird, rabbit
1. the fan of gospel is the owner of the ferret##1
2. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the fan of electronic is between the owner of the ferret and the fan of house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | punk   | gospel | electronic | house      |
| Pet     | bird | ferret    | goat  | rabbit |

