.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, lacrosse, soccer, weightlifting
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, lawyer, teacher, dressmaker
1. the mechanic is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the lawyer is between the person who's sport is soccer and the teacher##2
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
4. the mechanic is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | biathlon | weightlifting | soccer     | lacrosse   |
| Job   | teacher   | lawyer     | dressmaker | mechanic |

