.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, australian, italian, indian
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, scooter, ship, van
1. the italian is between the person driving the boat and the turkish##2
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the turkish##1
3. the indian is on the right of the turkish##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the van##1
5. the turkish is on the left of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Nationality         | australian | italian | turkish | indian |
| Transport   | boat         | van       | scooter    | ship         |

