.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, garlic, peach, plum
City: prague, nizza, hannover, new-york
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person eating plum##1
2. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person eating peach##1
3. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
4. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
5. the person traveling to nizza is between the person eating garlic and the person traveling to new-york##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | plum   | peach      | garlic   | avocado  |
| City   | new-york | nizza | hannover | prague |

