.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, rock-climbing, singing, writing
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, nigerian, brazilian, chinese
1. the brazilian is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the nigerian is on the left of the chinese##1
3. the argentine is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is the nigerian##1
5. the argentine is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the nigerian is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is writing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | singing | writing | filmmaking |
| Nationality   | brazilian          | nigerian     | chinese  | argentine     |

