4. the designer is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | designer | police-officer | musician | nurse     |
| Color   | grey   | fuchsia    | chestnut   | red |

