1. the egyptian is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the spanish is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the italian##2
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | spanish | italian | egyptian | pakistani |
| Hobby           | magic-tricks  | rock-climbing  | writing | fishing      |

