3. the gothic-revival house is between the person driving the bike and the modern house##2
4. the farmhouse house is the person driving the bike##1
5. the palace house is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| House       | farmhouse | gothic-revival | modern | palace |
| Transport   | bike    | roller  | skateboard    | ship       |

